data.description:
Great opportunity for a live-work office + home in a trendy upscale area. Perfect set-up for remote workers or entrepreneurs that hate commuting. Historic home zoned for both commercial and residential suitable for a multitude of uses. This property has all the benefits of being in the center of business plus a residential neighborhood feel surrounded by properties with the same charm and ambiance. The exterior features separate entrances for the upper and lower units, paved off street parking for 10 cars, and views of Mill Mountain and the Roanoke Star. Perfect for a medical office including physical therapist, counselors, attorney, insurance, or technical services. 
5 minutes (1.2mi) to Virginia Tech Carilion School of Medicine Teaching College. Excellent location for Bed and Breakfast, rentals for traveling nurses, spa, etc. Located in Roanoke's Opportunity Zone with the most flexible zoning district in Roanoke. 
Less than a mile to Downtown Roanoke with Farmer's Market, restaurants, shopping, and cultural opportunities.
6 miles to Roanoke Regional Airport
Located in an Opportunity Zone.

Walk score (80) very walkable
Bike score (75) very bikeable
The downstairs unit boasts original hardwood floors, ample office, reception, and conference space, full kitchen, and full bath. The upstairs unit includes 3 bedrooms, large dining room with built in corner cabinet, generously sized walk-in closet, full bath, and kitchen. Additional storage space is found in the basement of the property and has an outside entrance as well.

"	Upgrades include 
"	Plumbing replaced.
"	Electrical replaced (2)200amp services. 
"	Roof replaced with 35 yrs architectural shingles. 
"	Zoned heating & air  2 heat pumps. 
"	New tongue and groove flooring on front porch.
